(1352, 1972, '2022-09-27 11:47:19', '2022-09-27 11:47:19', 'Our Jazzedge resident drummer, Mike Marble, will be challenging your rhythm skills in this live training session. He will work with you on rhythm sight-reading and how to best interpret and perform all different types of rhythms. Rhythm is the backbone of music, and without good rhythm and time your playing will sound lackluster.\r\n\r\nThese ongoing live training sessions with Mike will both challenge and inspire your playing.\r\n\r\nCome ask your questions about rhythm, working with drummers, drumming or playing with a group. Mike has an expansive pedigree of performances with a wide range of musicians and performing multiple different styles of music ranging from jazz and rock to blues and funk.\r\n\r\n<strong>Here\'s what students have to say:</strong>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<div class=\"NC79P\"><em>\"That Live Rhythm Training was awesome! Mike Marble is not only a great teacher, but also a really good entertainer! We had so much fun! Adapted to piano players, his training is a perfect way to progress in terms of rhythm and also to better understand how a drummer reads rhythms, practices and performs. Highly recommended!\" </em></div></blockquote>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"Aovyg\" data-container=\"1977426874\" data-fieldid=\"1887114391\" data-supportembedding=\"true\">\r\n<div class=\"o5ddgd\">\r\n<div class=\"roun9\">\r\n<div id=\"c91\" class=\"rPU8He\" data-chart=\"1977426874\" data-fieldid=\"1887114391\">\r\n<div class=\"PlcjTc\">\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<div class=\"NC79P\">\r\n\r\n<em>\"Awesome opportunity to enter into a drummer\'s mind! In addition, rhythm being at the core of all music, everything we learn here is essential, whatever instrument we play!\"</em>\r\n<div class=\"NC79P\"><em>\"Just a huge thank you! I loved your teaching and the vibe you created, which is present in all your Lessons on Jazzedge Academy site! So essential to enjoy learning! Before the session, I was not sure how I would apply your teaching to my piano practice and you gave the answer right away! No doubt that I will progress through your teaching! Awesome!\"</em></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div></blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"Aovyg\" data-container=\"568612971\" data-fieldid=\"917039137\" data-supportembedding=\"true\">\r\n<div class=\"o5ddgd\">\r\n<div class=\"roun9\">\r\n<div class=\"HEC51d\">\r\n<div data-chartcontainer=\"568612971\">\r\n<div id=\"c94\" class=\"SLvR0\" role=\"heading\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Rhythm Training Class', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'rhythm-training', '', '', '2024-04-07 12:06:26', '2024-04-07 16:06:26', '', 0, 'https://jazzedge.academy/?post_type=event&#038;p=1352', 0, 'studio-event', '', 0),
