(2162, 1972, '2023-05-26 09:55:09', '2023-05-26 13:55:09', 'Come and share your playing and ask your questions. You are welcome to submit your question and video ahead of time by clicking \'Register For This Event\' in the sidebar.\r\n\r\nCoaching is optional and not required.\r\n\r\nYou <strong>do not</strong> have to share your video during coaching. You\'re in control! Come and observe if you are nervous.\r\n\r\nWe\'re all friends here and coaching is designed to be an easy-going, low stress experience!', 'Coaching with Paul', '', 'draft', 'open', 'closed', '', 'coaching-with-paul-2', '', '', '2024-09-03 13:36:25', '2024-09-03 13:36:25', '', 0, 'https://jazzedge.academy/event/coaching-with-paul-2/', 0, 'studio-event', '', 0),
