(2455, 1972, '2023-10-04 12:43:10', '2023-10-04 16:43:10', 'In this class we will be working on creating a beginner arrangement for a classic \"standard\" song. We will couple this with The Confident Improviser™ class to also learn improvisation and the \"Practical Music Theory &amp; Reharmonization\" class to learn about harmony, analysis and music theory.', 'Just Standards (Beginner)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'just-standards-beginner-11', '', '', '2024-04-07 12:15:53', '2024-04-07 16:15:53', '', 0, 'https://jazzedge.academy/event/just-standards-beginner-11/', 0, 'studio-event', '', 0),
