(2507, 1972, '2023-10-23 16:52:53', '2023-10-23 20:52:53', 'Our Jazzedge resident drummer, Mike Marble, will be challenging your rhythm skills in this live training session. He will work with you on rhythm sight-reading and how to best interpret and perform all different types of rhythms. Rhythm is the backbone of music, and without good rhythm and time your playing will sound lackluster.\r\n\r\nThese ongoing live training sessions with Mike will both challenge and inspire your playing.\r\n\r\nCome ask your questions about rhythm, working with drummers, drumming or playing with a group. Mike has an expansive pedigree of performances with a wide range of musicians and performing multiple different styles of music ranging from jazz and rock to blues and funk.\r\n\r\n<strong>Here\'s what students have to say:</strong>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<div class=\"NC79P\"><em>\"That Live Rhythm Training was awesome! Mike Marble is not only a great teacher, but also a really good entertainer! We had so much fun! Adapted to piano players, his training is a perfect way to progress in terms of rhythm and also to better understand how a drummer reads rhythms, practices and performs. Highly recommended!\" </em></div></blockquote>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"Aovyg\" data-container=\"1977426874\" data-fieldid=\"1887114391\" data-supportembedding=\"true\">\r\n<div class=\"o5ddgd\">\r\n<div class=\"roun9\">\r\n<div id=\"c91\" class=\"rPU8He\" data-chart=\"1977426874\" data-fieldid=\"1887114391\">\r\n<div class=\"PlcjTc\">\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<div class=\"NC79P\">\r\n\r\n<em>\"Awesome opportunity to enter into a drummer\'s mind! In addition, rhythm being at the core of all music, everything we learn here is essential, whatever instrument we play!\"</em>\r\n<div class=\"NC79P\"><em>\"Just a huge thank you! I loved your teaching and the vibe you created, which is present in all your Lessons on Jazzedge Academy site! So essential to enjoy learning! Before the session, I was not sure how I would apply your teaching to my piano practice and you gave the answer right away! No doubt that I will progress through your teaching! Awesome!\"</em></div>\r\n</div></blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/877274473?h=ef1fdda2e1\"></iframe>', 'Rhythm Training Class', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'rhythm-training-class', '', '', '2024-04-07 12:15:55', '2024-04-07 16:15:55', '', 0, 'https://jazzedge.academy/?post_type=event&#038;p=2507', 0, 'studio-event', '', 0),
(2525, 1972, '2023-10-30 03:48:43', '2023-10-30 07:48:43', 'Learn how to improvise over our \"Just Standards\" songs in this class.\r\n\r\nThis is an <strong>advanced-level class</strong> so you should have already gone through several major scales and know your chords.\r\n\r\nTo get ready for this class, be sure to <a href=\"https://jazzedge.academy/lesson/nbgjp-preparation-lesson/\">work through these preparation lessons</a>.\r\n\r\nIt is also a great idea to work through <a href=\"https://jazzedge.academy/course/the-confident-improviser-level-1/\">The Confident Improviser™ - Level 1</a>.\r\n\r\nIn this class, you\'ll learn:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Scales and \"ingredients\" for improvising</li>\r\n 	<li>How to use rhythm in your improvisation</li>\r\n 	<li>How to create licks and variations</li>\r\n 	<li>How to apply your improvisation skills to other styles (i.e. rock, pop, gospel, blues, latin and more)</li>\r\n 	<li>Exercises to practice to stay on track</li>\r\n</ul>', 'The Confident Improviser - Advanced', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'the-confident-improviser-advanced-5', '', '', '2024-04-07 12:15:54', '2024-04-07 16:15:54', '', 0, 'https://jazzedge.academy/event/the-confident-improviser-advanced-5/', 0, 'studio-event', '', 0),
(2533, 1972, '2023-11-02 15:06:05', '2023-11-02 19:06:05', 'Unleash Your Inner Maestro with the Creative Pianist Toolkit™!\r\n\r\nEmbark on a musical journey that will transform the way you play and perceive piano music. The Creative Pianist Toolkit™ is not just a set of classes; it\'s your roadmap to mastering the piano with flair and creativity.\r\n\r\n🎼 <strong>Dive into Three Dynamic Classes:</strong>\r\n\r\n1. <strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Theory/Reharm</span></strong>: Unlock the secrets of music theory to deeply understand and interpret music. We\'ll guide you through the art of tune analysis, effective memorization, and crafting reharmonizations that breathe new life into classic melodies.\r\n\r\n2. <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Standards</strong></span>: Journey across genres from jazz to pop, rock to Latin. Start with simple arrangements and progress to sophisticated performances that will captivate any audience. We will cover both beginner and advanced arrangements in this class! Your friends and family won\'t believe their ears!\r\n\r\n3. <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Improvisation</strong></span>: Break free from the written notes and improvise with confidence. Apply the skills from our Theory and Standards classes to discover improvisation techniques that transcend song boundaries and genres.\r\n\r\n🌟 <strong>Open to All Levels</strong>: Whether you\'re just starting out or have years of experience, these classes will challenge and inspire you. We recommend having at least a year of piano experience, but if you\'re a complete novice, begin your adventure with our 30-Day Piano Playbook™.\r\n\r\n👨‍🏫 <strong>Expert Guidance from Willie</strong>: No matter your level, Willie\'s dual-track teaching approach ensures you\'ll find material tailored to your skills. Plus, get a weekly practice plan to keep your fingers dancing on the keys, <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">even when you\